532
00:40:24,612 --> 00:40:27,512
The problem is, we don't have a construction company.

533
00:40:27,512 --> 00:40:29,711
Are you going to shovel yourself, Fellow Korean Lad?

534
00:40:29,711 --> 00:40:31,012
I asked her to check for a construction company

535
00:40:31,012 --> 00:40:32,852
that we can buy.

536
00:40:32,852 --> 00:40:36,952
   

537
00:40:36,952 --> 00:40:38,361
   

538
00:40:38,361 --> 00:40:42,062
