548
00:41:02,351 --> 00:41:05,122
It’s the trifecta: breach of fiduciary duty, embezzlement, and even accounting fraud.

549
00:41:05,122 --> 00:41:06,421
They must be over-stating actual construction costs

550
00:41:06,421 --> 00:41:08,222
and fixing the prices as well.

551
00:41:08,222 --> 00:41:09,722
Construction companies are the easiest

552
00:41:09,722 --> 00:41:11,251
to make money without labels.

553
00:41:11,251 --> 00:41:12,922
Bingo.

554
00:41:22,372 --> 00:41:25,322
How could you join Soonyang Construction

555
00:41:25,322 --> 00:41:29,951
without discussing with me and as you like?

556
00:41:30,841 --> 00:41:32,241
At this critical time?

557
00:41:32,241 --> 00:41:36,691
Right now, we should acquire more shares in Soonyang Corporation.

558
00:41:37,481 --> 00:41:43,081
Before the succession plan is finalized, Grandfather could pass away.

559
00:41:43,081 --> 00:41:44,952
- What? 
 - The budget

560
00:41:44,952 --> 00:41:48,202
for the New Seoul Town project is five trillion won  ($5B) ,

561
00:41:48,202 --> 00:41:52,761
which means we can stash much more money away as a slush fund.

562
00:41:52,761 --> 00:41:55,532
Then you joined Soonyang Construction because...

