00:41:57,031 --> 00:42:01,171
I know I always made you anxious, just like now.

564
00:42:02,012 --> 00:42:05,912
That you'd fall out of favor with Grandpa because of me.

565
00:42:05,912 --> 00:42:09,591
You were afraid I'd ruin your plan to succeed the throne.

566
00:42:11,012 --> 00:42:14,151
- Seong Jun, that's... 
 - Father.

567
00:42:15,921 --> 00:42:19,222
Now, I can really understand you.

568
00:42:20,092 --> 00:42:23,262
I feel exactly the same way right now.

569
00:42:52,922 --> 00:42:56,350
   

570
00:42:57,522 --> 00:42:59,161
   

