768
00:57:10,412 --> 00:57:14,581
Why? Will you tell the prosecution?

769
00:57:22,961 --> 00:57:28,562
Do you think they'll side with you?

770
00:57:28,562 --> 00:57:32,802
Which is why I plan to hold a press conference as soon as I leave Jeongsimjae.

771
00:57:32,802 --> 00:57:35,641
It'll be broadcast live on the Internet.

772
00:57:36,912 --> 00:57:42,441
As the conglomerate hunter and your son-in-law, I plan to tell the truth.

773
00:57:46,852 --> 00:57:52,521
Do you think public opinion will side with you, Father?

774
00:58:14,611 --> 00:58:20,081
They say you can never win against your children.

775
00:58:21,952 --> 00:58:24,602
My son-in-law is my child, too, after all.

776
00:58:27,222 --> 00:58:29,961
How could I win against you?

777
00:58:34,461 --> 00:58:41,971
Then I need you to promise me something.

