00:59:03,792 --> 00:59:06,262
Nephew, you were right.

779
00:59:06,262 --> 00:59:09,231
I did exactly as you said, and he gave me the go-ahead.

780
00:59:09,231 --> 00:59:11,332
Grandpa...

781
00:59:11,332 --> 00:59:13,522
- Grandpa gave you the go-ahead? 
 - Yes.

782
00:59:14,202 --> 00:59:15,742
That's great. Congratulations, Uncle Chang Je.

783
00:59:15,742 --> 00:59:17,272
Gosh, thanks.

784
00:59:17,272 --> 00:59:19,842
- Best of luck. 
 - Thanks.

785
00:59:20,481 --> 00:59:22,582
- Hey, nephew. 
 - Yes?

786
00:59:22,582 --> 00:59:26,512
I didn't think you'd help me.

787
00:59:26,512 --> 00:59:29,651
Why did you help me?

788
00:59:32,051 --> 00:59:35,251
Well, the title of mayor of Seoul suits you better

789
00:59:35,251 --> 00:59:38,392
than a mere son-in-law of the Soonyang family,

790
00:59:39,191 --> 00:59:40,931
Uncle Chang Je.

791
00:59:57,781 --> 01:00:01,452
Did you give him the go-ahead to run for mayor?

792
01:00:02,952 --> 01:00:05,522
Will that be all right, Sir?

793
01:00:06,691 --> 01:00:08,791
What can I do?

794
01:00:10,662 --> 01:00:18,112
I shall try to use the poultry knife to butcher a cow.

795
01:00:25,312 --> 01:00:30,582
Someone's got Chang Je's back.

796
01:00:31,881 --> 01:00:37,331
Hang Jae, I need you to find out who it is,

797
01:00:37,331 --> 01:00:41,562
and why they're trying to make Chang Je the mayor of Seoul.

798
01:00:42,791 --> 01:00:44,641
   

799
01:00:44,641 --> 01:00:47,062
 Seoul, Choi Chang Je. 53.6 percent. 

800
01:00:47,062 --> 01:00:49,262
 Yang Doo Yeong, 41.7 percent. 

801
01:00:49,262 --> 01:00:50,731
- Yes! 
 - Yes.

802
01:00:50,731 --> 01:00:52,401
 Six from the United Liberal Democrats. 

803
01:00:52,401 --> 01:00:53,971
 Four from the Korea Party. 

804
01:00:53,971 --> 01:00:55,142
- Cheers. 
 - Cheers.

805
01:00:55,142 --> 01:00:56,642
Cheers.

806
01:00:56,642 --> 01:01:00,811
 Choi Chang Je from the New Democratic Korea Party has won the election. 

807
01:01:00,811 --> 01:01:02,952
Now that we have the mayor of Seoul on our side,

808
01:01:02,952 --> 01:01:04,912
we just need Mayor Choi

809
01:01:04,912 --> 01:01:10,251
to give the New Seoul Town project to us, Jaea Construction.

810
01:01:10,251 --> 01:01:12,822
We can trust him, right?

811
01:01:12,822 --> 01:01:14,522
I mean, we're dealing with Jin Yang Cheol here.

812
01:01:14,522 --> 01:01:18,230
Mayor Choi is a softie. Would he be able to handle him?

813
01:01:19,272 --> 01:01:23,231
My gosh. Congratulations, Chang Je.

814
01:01:23,231 --> 01:01:25,172
But as you know,

815
01:01:25,172 --> 01:01:28,972
you are and will always be my one and only son-in-law

816
01:01:28,972 --> 01:01:33,572
whom I'm very proud of, no matter where you are or what you do.

817
01:01:33,572 --> 01:01:35,012
Don't forget that.

818
01:01:35,012 --> 01:01:37,512
 Thank you. I'll never forget that. 

819
01:01:37,512 --> 01:01:40,122
 - Choi Chang Je! 
 - Hurrah! 

820
01:01:40,122 --> 01:01:41,851
 - Hurrah! 
 - Hurrah! 

821
01:01:41,851 --> 01:01:44,992
 - Mayor of Seoul, Choi Chang Je! 
 - Mayor of Seoul, Choi Chang Je! 

822
01:01:44,992 --> 01:01:46,840
 - Yes! 
 - Mayor Choi Chang Je! 

823
01:01:46,840 --> 01:01:51,050
   

824
01:02:01,272 --> 01:02:03,242
As for the New Seoul Town project,

825
01:02:03,242 --> 01:02:04,841
the bidding results should've been announced already.

826
01:02:04,841 --> 01:02:09,212
But Junior Managing Director Jin Seong Jun hasn't called yet, Sir.

827
01:02:09,212 --> 01:02:11,751
There he is.

828
01:02:19,551 --> 01:02:21,722
So how did it go?

829
01:02:22,461 --> 01:02:25,411
The New Seoul Town development project

830
01:02:28,432 --> 01:02:31,101
has gone to Jea Construction.

831
01:02:32,671 --> 01:02:34,371
Sir.

832
01:02:43,211 --> 01:02:46,282
Tell Son-in-law Chang Je that I want to see him.

833
01:03:34,702 --> 01:03:36,961
You're here.

834
01:03:43,372 --> 01:03:48,282
I wanted to wait outside to welcome the new mayor.

835
01:03:48,941 --> 01:03:51,381
Let's go inside.

836
01:03:51,381 --> 01:03:55,122
Why don't we just talk here?

837
01:04:04,031 --> 01:04:08,962
My new job is keeping me busy, Father.

838
01:04:14,842 --> 01:04:16,442
Who is it?

839
01:04:18,211 --> 01:04:22,840
Who is backing you that you can be this arrogant?

840
01:04:25,912 --> 01:04:30,981
You gave the New Seoul Town project to Jea Construction.

841
01:04:30,981 --> 01:04:33,342
Did that person put you up to it?

842
01:04:36,162 --> 01:04:39,432
The person behind you.

843
01:04:44,231 --> 01:04:46,472
Is it Miracle?

844
01:04:52,272 --> 01:04:55,182
I guess you didn't know.

845
01:04:56,582 --> 01:05:04,532
The people who have my back are... the ten million citizens of Seoul.

846
01:05:06,351 --> 01:05:07,691
What?

847
01:05:07,691 --> 01:05:10,631
As the mayor of Seoul, I chose Jea Construction

848
01:05:10,631 --> 01:05:12,761
over Soonyang according to the fair rules and procedures,

849
01:05:12,761 --> 01:05:15,932
for the sake of Seoul's better future.

850
01:05:17,102 --> 01:05:20,431
Should you have any other official questions,

851
01:05:20,431 --> 01:05:24,372
I will see you in my office next time, Chairman.

852
01:05:55,671 --> 01:06:00,841
Jea Construction got the New Seoul Town project?

853
01:06:03,912 --> 01:06:06,562
It was Mr. Jin Seong Jun's first project.

854
01:06:06,562 --> 01:06:08,122
He must be very disappointed.

855
01:06:08,122 --> 01:06:11,392
And I guess he's preparing to go study abroad or something.

856
01:06:11,392 --> 01:06:14,322
He frequents a language institute.

857
01:06:22,961 --> 01:06:24,701
That's interesting.

858
01:06:24,701 --> 01:06:28,841
Miracle Investment has control over Jea Construction.

859
01:06:28,841 --> 01:06:32,951
Miracle and Jin Do Jun's language institute are in the same building.

860
01:06:35,041 --> 01:06:40,882
I believe in fate but not in coincidences.

861
01:06:41,821 --> 01:06:42,881
We're from the prosecution.

862
01:06:42,881 --> 01:06:45,222
We're here to conduct a search and seizure.

863
01:06:45,222 --> 01:06:46,892
- Search the office. 
 - Yes, Sir.

864
01:06:46,892 --> 01:06:49,292
- Start over there. 
 - Over here.

865
01:06:51,831 --> 01:06:54,262
Excuse me. Who are you?

866
01:06:54,262 --> 01:06:56,362
Is Mr. Oh Se Hyeon here?

867
01:06:56,362 --> 01:06:58,271
What is this about?

868
01:06:58,271 --> 01:07:00,872
We're from the Seoul District Public Prosecutors' Office.

869
01:07:00,872 --> 01:07:03,972
We received a tip-off that you paid a large bribe

870
01:07:03,972 --> 01:07:09,072
to Mayor Choi Chang Je to land the New Seoul Town project.

871
01:07:16,722 --> 01:07:21,410
   

872
01:07:42,311 --> 01:07:46,981
My, Soonyang sure has a lot of power.

873
01:07:46,981 --> 01:07:50,322
Even prosecutors are at their beck and call.

874
01:07:51,451 --> 01:07:53,601
What do you want from me?

875
01:07:54,321 --> 01:08:00,121
Chairman Jin wants to meet the majority shareholder of Miracle.

876
01:08:00,901 --> 01:08:02,901
The real owner of the company.

877
01:08:55,182 --> 01:08:58,151
You know Miracle Investment, right?

878
01:08:59,091 --> 01:09:05,792
Then do you also know who the company's real owner is?

879
01:09:05,792 --> 01:09:08,712
You're talking like you know who it is.

880
01:09:08,712 --> 01:09:10,601
Who is it?

881
01:11:04,551 --> 01:11:06,701
I'm Miracle's majority shareholder,

882
01:11:07,551 --> 01:11:09,752
Jin Do Jun.

883
01:11:18,961 --> 01:11:24,110
   

884
01:11:25,040 --> 01:11:32,000


885
01:11:53,431 --> 01:11:57,201
 Why? Why did you do such a thing? 

886
01:11:57,201 --> 01:12:01,671
 I'd like to buy... Soonyang. 

887
01:12:01,671 --> 01:12:03,542
 I'm worried. 

888
01:12:03,542 --> 01:12:06,071
 He will try to drag me down throughout my term. 

889
01:12:06,071 --> 01:12:10,360
 Then soar high enough so he can't drag you down. 

890
01:12:11,741 --> 01:12:15,751
 Be honest with me. You're not 22, right? 

891
01:12:15,751 --> 01:12:18,152
 You said partners must be honest with each other. 

892
01:12:18,152 --> 01:12:21,622
 We'll be good partners. 

893
01:12:21,622 --> 01:12:25,891
 It sure is an offer I can't refuse. 

894
01:12:25,891 --> 01:12:27,702
 We've got a problem. 

895
01:12:27,702 --> 01:12:31,602
 They contacted us and said they'd cancel the plan to enter DMC altogether. 

896
01:12:31,602 --> 01:12:37,090
 My eldest grandson, do you want to get your revenge? 

897
01:12:37,090 --> 01:12:43,280
♫  Love for me forever  ♫

